gaffer.function.context

Class ConsumerProducerFunctionContext<R,F extends ConsumerProducerFunction>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gaffer.function.context.FunctionContext<F>
      • gaffer.function.context.ConsumerFunctionContext<R,F>
        • gaffer.function.context.ConsumerProducerFunctionContext<R,F>
  • Type Parameters:
    R - The type of reference used to select from and project into tuples in this context.
    F - The type of ConsumerProducerFunction wrapped by the context.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ConsumerProducerFunctionContext<R,F extends ConsumerProducerFunction>
extends ConsumerFunctionContext<R,F>
    A ConsumerProducerFunctionContext extends a ConsumerFunctionContext to wrap a ConsumerProducerFunction and also provide the references to project the results produced by the function into an output Tuple.
